The system uses a .env file for email configuration. As per security concerns, the gmail account name and app password has to be configured while testing.

To enable email notifications:

1. Use a Gmail account

Replace:
MAIL_USERNAME=yourname@gmail.com
MAIL_FROM=yourname@gmail.com
with gmail account name

2. Generate App Password
   Go to Google Account → Security
   Enable 2-Step Verification
   Create App Password

3. Then update:

MAIL_PASSWORD=your_generated_app_password
